<paragraph id="8B9A517BFFB2FFB8FF5F4314FD60EEC2" blockId="22.[151,1436,1913,2010]" box="[199,698,1913,1938]" pageId="22" pageNumber="55">
<emphasis id="B9518D69FFB2FFB8FF5F4314FE6BEEC2" bold="true" box="[199,433,1913,1938]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="55" reason="1">Material examined.</emphasis>
See 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB42C8AFFB2FFB8FE7E4314FD6CEEC2" author="Kronestedt, T." box="[486,694,1913,1938]" pageId="22" pageNumber="55" pagination="281 - 290" refId="ref14176" refString="Kronestedt, T. (2004) Studies on species of Holarctic Pardosa groups (Araneae, Lycosidae). VI. On the identity of Pardosa luciae Tongiorgi with notes on P. trailli (O. P. - Cambridge) and some other species in the P. nigra - group. Denisia, 12, 281 - 290." type="journal article" year="2004">Kronestedt (2004)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
